Sony has launched new colourful DualShock 4 controllers for the PlayStation 4. “We’re happy to announce that four new vibrant and stylish colours are joining the DualShock 4 wireless controller line-up in September – Berry Blue, Sunset Orange, Blue Camouflage, and Copper,” said the company. The new colors will be available across retailers in the US for $64.99, while stocks last. Sony did not mention any details about the controllers being available outside of North America at the time of publication. Images of the new controllers are posted below.    